title: Family Guy The Quest for Stuff v1.5.9 [Mod]
description:
WHAT'S NEW
Merry Christmas and Happy Hanukkah! 'Tis the season of giving, unless you're Peter Griffin. For him, it's the season of pissing off the Giant Chicken and ruining Christmas. Lois and Santa need your help delivering a successful holiday season by decorating the town and making gifts!
Santa's reindeer are on strike, putting a wrench in that whole delivering presents thing. It's cool, though, there's a plan B! You can now send gifts to your friends with our new Secret Santa feature.

Mod
Free shopping and rushing
